OUR SERVICES
Smart, scalable services crafted for todays forward-thinkers.
Growth Equity

Growth equity is a type of private investment, usually a minority investment, in relatively mature companies that are looking for capital to expand or restructure operations, enter new markets, or finance a significant acquisition without a change of control of the business.

Corporate Restructuring

We offer corporate restructuring services to help businesses overcome financial and operational challenges. Our tailored strategies focus on reducing risk, preserving value, and optimizing capital structures. With a collaborative approach, we support long-term stability and business resilience.

Takeovers

We offer end-to-end advisory services for takeovers, guiding clients through opportunity identification, target evaluation, and seamless execution. Our expertise spans both friendly and hostile takeovers, backed by thorough due diligence and regulatory compliance. With a focus on value creation, we help ensure successful integration and strategic growth.

Capital Markets Advisory

We offer independent advisory for a broad range of capital market transactions, including IPOs, private placements, rights issues, and strategic buybacks. Our expertise ensures efficient execution and tailored solutions that enhance financial performance, maximize shareholder value, and strengthen your market presence for long-term success.
Venture Capital

Our private equity division invests in both private and publicly listed companies, independently or alongside venture capital funds, AIFs, and other investors. We focus on innovation and strategic growth across sectors, turning potential into performance and creating lasting value for investors and stakeholders.

M&A Advisory

At SKY Bridge Incap Advisory LLP, we deliver specialized M&A services aligned with your strategic vision. From strategic advisory and accurate valuations to due diligence, negotiation support, and regulatory compliance, our end-to-end solutions ensure seamless execution and long-term value creation.

Buyout and Strategic Joint Ventures

We specialize in consortium investments by partnering with leading private equity firms to acquire stakes in high-potential companies. Our collaborative model enables shared risk, resource pooling, and strategic investment in large, complex deals. We also co-invest with promoters in joint ventures, offering project funding and driving success through aligned interests.

Wealth Planning

Wealth planning helps individuals and families structure their finances to achieve long-term goals, including retirement, estate planning, and tax optimization.
